name: Tropical Darkness
description:
Physical hand drawn A4 size Ink drawing/painting.
As the sky turns red
And the air becomes still
All the animals and insects become aware
What is about to happen in the underbrush?
Is danger lurking?
A position of safety needs to be reached before the decimation takes place.
Is there time?

A4 physical ink piece which has been scanned at 600dpi, and digitally enhanced. 4566 x 6930 pixels.
